snippet.title: Iron Village Alpha Demo - Now on Steam!
snippet.description:
This is Iron Village, an upcoming cozy town builder game... with trains! The demo is now available on Steam! https://store.steampowered.com/app/3011060/Iron_Village/

Join us on Discord: https://discord.com/invite/wF7HJbvRGF
